      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the assembly line! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels practically brand new, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
