    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, showcasing impeccable mechanical and cosmetic preservation. This example features the legendary S65B40 naturally aspirated V8, delivering a razor-sharp throttle response and an 8,250 RPM redline. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides seamless torque transfer to the variable M differential lock. This vehicle boasts a documented service history with proactive rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service already completed. The factory-original paint retains its deep luster with no signs of panel misalignment, while the undercarriage remains free of oxidation. Equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and Competition Package wheels, this chassis offers unparalleled lateral grip and dampening precision. A truly pristine specimen for the most demanding collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
