    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a true collector-grade specimen, maintained with an obsessive attention to detail that is immediately apparent. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or any surface imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, and the alloy wheels are pristine, showing no signs of curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin is a time-capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and taut, with no creasing on the bolsters or wear on the touchpoints. All onboard electronics, including the high-fidelity audio system and multi-zone climate control, operate with crisp, factory-new precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced strictly according to a preventative maintenance schedule. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is as clean as the day it left the assembly line. Included are all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a comprehensive binder of service records. This is a turn-key example for the discerning buyer who demands a vehicle in showroom condition.",
